3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper discusses the interrelation between two phenomena observed in complex networks, which is relevant to the networking and internet architecture subfield.
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper introduces certain measures related to the analysis of complex systems, which could be relevant to the systems and control subfield.
5. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper discusses the analysis of complex networks, which is a common topic in the machine learning subfield, particularly in the context of graph-based learning algorithms.
